---
title: Turkey Bulgogi Bowls with Carrots, Pickled Cucumber & Sriracha Crema
description: If you can’t seem to get enough of Korean-inspired flavors, bulgogi is sure to leave you satisfied. This dish centers around pork cooked in a sesame and soy sauce marinade with a little bit of peppery sweetness.There’s also crisp quick-pickled cucumbers, tender carrots, and spicy crema, all served over fluffy rice—each bowl is jam-packed with flavor!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/63ebf8c97204705e2a01691e-0c87e3ff.jpg
